DESCRIPTION:Doors open 30mins before the performance. Free Seating.

Once again the popular Southwark Sinfonietta will close the Festival with a performance of classical music.

Vaughan Williams - The Wasps
 
Faure - Pelleas et Melisande
 
Imogen Holst - On Westhall Hill
 
Mendelssohn - Symphony No.3 'Scottish'
